import { formatCurrency } from "../helpers/number-helper" import { useHistory } from "react-router-dom" import { Table } from "semantic-ui-react" import moment from "moment" const OrderItem = ({ order }) => { const history = useHistory() return ( {order.orderId} {order.shopName} {order.phoneNumberOfShop} {formatCurrency(order.totalPrice)} {moment(order.orderTime).format("DD MMM, YYYY")} {order.status} {" "}
history.push("/order/" + order.orderId)} > View Order
) } export default OrderItem
